```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Game Hub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4a6fa5;
            --secondary: #166088;
            --accent: #4fc3a1;
            --dark: #2d3047;
            --light: #f8f9fa;
            --wrong: #ff6b6b;
            --correct: #51cf66;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #e4e8f0 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-weight: 300;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .score-display {
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .score-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .score-value {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .score-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .tab-container {
            display: flex;
            background: var(--light);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .tab {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--dark);
            position: relative;
        }

        .tab:hover {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .tab.active {
            background: white;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .tab.active::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -1px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--accent);
        }

        .game-container {
            display: none;
            padding: 2rem;
            min-height: 500px;
        }

        .game-container.active {
            display: block;
        }

        .game-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--dark);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .game-info {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        .game-info.highlight {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* Tic-Tac-Toe Styles */
        .tic-tac-toe-board {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            aspect-ratio: 1/1;
        }

        .cell {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.2s;
            aspect-ratio: 1/1;
        }

        .cell:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .cell.x { color: var(--primary); }
        .cell.o { color: var(--secondary); }

        /* Memory Game Styles */
        .memory-board {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            aspect-ratio: 1/1;
            position: relative;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
        }

        .card-face {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .card-front {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: white;
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
        }

        .card-back {
            background: white;
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        .card.flipped {
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
        }

        .card.matched {
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(79, 195, 161, 0.5);
        }

        /* Number Guessing Styles */
        .guess-container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .guess-input-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .guess-input {
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 120px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .guess-input:focus {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(79, 195, 161, 0.2);
        }

        .guess-btn {
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .guess-btn:hover {
            background: #3da58a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .guess-history {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .guess-item {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .guess-item.low {
            background: var(--wrong);
            color: white;
        }

        .guess-item.high {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
        }

        .guess-item.correct {
            background: var(--correct);
            color: white;
            animation: celebrate 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes celebrate {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* Controls */
        .controls {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #3da58a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #e2e6ea;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .memory-board {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }

            .score-display {
                position: static;
                transform: none;
                justify-content: center;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .tab {
                padding: 0.8rem 0.5rem;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .memory-board {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1><i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i> Game Hub</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Three fun games in one place!</p>
            <div class="score-display">
                <div class="score-item">
                    <div class="score-value" id="tic-tac-toe-score">0</div>
                    <div class="score-label">Tic-Tac-Toe Wins</div>
                </div>
                <div class="score-item">
                    <div class="score-value" id="memory-score">0</div>
                    <div class="score-label">Memory Pairs</div>
                </div>
                <div class="score-item">
                    <div class="score-value" id="guess-score">0</div>
                    <div class="score-label">Guesses</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="tab-container">
            <div class="tab active" onclick="openGame('tic-tac-toe')">
                <i class="fas fa-times"></i> Tic-Tac-Toe
            </div>
            <div class="tab" onclick="openGame('memory')">
                <i class="fas fa-brain"></i> Memory
            </div>
            <div class="tab" onclick="openGame('guess')">
                <i class="fas fa-question"></i> Guessing
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tic-Tac-Toe Game -->
        <div id="tic-tac-toe" class="game-container active">
            <div class="game-header">
                <h2>Tic-Tac-Toe</h2>
                <div class="game-info" id="tic-tac-toe-info">Player X's turn</div>
            </div>

            <div class="tic-tac-toe-board" id="board">
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(0)"></div>
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(1)"></div>
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(2)"></div>
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(3)"></div>
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(4)"></div>
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(5)"></div>
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(6)"></div>
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(7)"></div>
                <div class="cell" onclick="makeMove(8)"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="controls">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="resetTicTacToe()">
                    <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Restart
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="toggleAIMode()" id="ai-toggle">
                    <i class="fas fa-robot"></i> AI: Off
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Memory Game -->
        <div id="memory" class="game-container">
            <div class="game-header">
                <h2>Memory Game</h2>
                <div class="game-info" id="memory-info">Find all matching pairs!</div>
            </div>

            <div class="memory-board" id="memory-board"></div>

            <div class="controls">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="setupMemoryGame()">
                    <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> New Game
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="toggleDifficulty()" id="difficulty-toggle">
                    <i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Difficulty: Medium
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Number Guessing Game -->
        <div id="guess" class="game-container">
            <div class="game-header">
                <h2>Number Guessing</h2>
                <div class="game-info" id="guess-info">Guess a number 1-100</div>
            </div>

            <div class="guess-container">
                <div class="guess-input-container">
                    <input type="number" class="guess-input" id="guess-input" min="1" max="100" placeholder="1-100">
                    <button class="guess-btn" onclick="checkGuess()">Submit</button>
                </div>

                <div class="guess-history" id="guess-history"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="controls">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="setupGuessGame()">
                    <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> New Game
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="showHint()">
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Hint
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Global scores
        const scores = {
            ticTacToe: { x: 0, o: 0 },
            memory: 0,
            guess: { wins: 0, totalGuesses: 0 }
        };

        // Tab navigation
        function openGame(gameName) {
            const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab');
            const containers = document.querySelectorAll('.game-container');

            tabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
            containers.forEach(container => container.classList.remove('active'));

            event.currentTarget.classList.add('active');
            document.getElementById(gameName).classList.add('active');

            // Special setup when switching to certain games
            if (gameName === 'memory' && !document.querySelector('.card')) {
                setupMemoryGame();
            }
        }

        // Tic-Tac-Toe Game
        let currentPlayer = 'X';
        let board = ['', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''];
        let gameActive = true;
        let aiMode = false;

        function makeMove(index) {
            if (!gameActive || board[index] !== '') return;

            // Human move
            board[index] = currentPlayer;
            updateCell(index, currentPlayer);

            if (checkWin()) {
                endGame(`Player ${currentPlayer} wins!`);
                if (currentPlayer === 'X') scores.ticTacToe.x++;
                else scores.ticTacToe.o++;
                updateScores();
                return;
            }

            if (checkDraw()) {
                endGame("It's a draw!");
                return;
            }

            switchPlayer();

            // AI move
            if (aiMode && currentPlayer === 'O' && gameActive) {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    const bestMove = findBestMove();
                    board[bestMove] = 'O';
                    updateCell(bestMove, 'O');

                    if (checkWin()) {
                        endGame("AI wins!");
                        scores.ticTacToe.o++;
                        updateScores();
                        return;
                    }

                    if (checkDraw()) {
                        endGame("It's a draw!");
                        return;
                    }

                    switchPlayer();
                }, 500);
            }
        }

        function updateCell(index, player) {
            const cell = document.querySelectorAll('.cell')[index];
            cell.textContent = player;
            cell.classList.add(player.toLowerCase());
        }

        function checkWin() {
            const winPatterns = [
                [0, 1, 2], [3, 4, 5], [6, 7, 8], // rows
                [0, 3, 6], [1, 4, 7], [2, 5, 8], // columns
                [0, 4, 8], [2, 4, 6]             // diagonals
            ];

            return winPatterns.some(pattern => {
                return pattern.every(index => {
                    return board[index] === currentPlayer;
                });
            });
        }

        function checkDraw() {
            return board.every(cell => cell !== '');
        }

        function switchPlayer() {
            currentPlayer = currentPlayer === 'X' ? 'O' : 'X';
            document.getElementById('tic-tac-toe-info').textContent = `Player ${currentPlayer}'s turn`;
        }

        function endGame(message) {
            gameActive = false;
            const infoElement = document.getElementById('tic-tac-toe-info');
            infoElement.textContent = message;
            infoElement.classList.add('highlight');
        }

        function resetTicTacToe() {
            board = ['', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''];
            currentPlayer = 'X';
            gameActive = true;

            document.querySelectorAll('.cell').forEach(cell => {
                cell.textContent = '';
                cell.classList.remove('x', 'o');
            });

            const infoElement = document.getElementById('tic-tac-toe-info');
            infoElement.textContent = "Player X's turn";
            infoElement.classList.remove('highlight');
        }

        function toggleAIMode() {
            aiMode = !aiMode;
            const button = document.getElementById('ai-toggle');
            button.innerHTML = `<i class="fas fa-robot"></i> AI: ${aiMode ? 'On' : 'Off'}`;
            resetTicTacToe();
        }

        // Simple AI using minimax algorithm
        function findBestMove() {
            // Check for immediate win
            for (let i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
                if (board[i] === '') {
                    board[i] = 'O';
                    if (checkWin()) {
                        board[i] = '';
                        return i;
                    }
                    board[i] = '';
                }
            }

            // Block opponent's immediate win
            for (let i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
                if (board[i] === '') {
                    board[i] = 'X';
                    if (checkWin()) {
                        board[i] = '';
                        return i;
                    }
                    board[i] = '';
                }
            }

            // Try to take center
            if (board[4] === '') return 4;

            // Try to take a corner
            const corners = [0, 2, 6, 8];
            const availableCorners = corners.filter(i => board[i] === '');
            if (availableCorners.length > 0) {
                return availableCorners[Math.floor(Math.random() * availableCorners.length)];
            }

            // Take any available edge
            const edges = [1, 3, 5, 7];
            const availableEdges = edges.filter(i => board[i] === '');
            if (availableEdges.length > 0) {
                return availableEdges[Math.floor(Math.random() * availableEdges.length)];
            }

            // Shouldn't reach here if game isn't over
            return board.indexOf('');
        }

        // Memory Game
        let memoryCards = [];
        let flippedCards = [];
        let matchedPairs = 0;
        let difficulty = 'medium'; // 'easy', 'medium', 'hard'
        const symbols = ['ðŸŽ', 'ðŸŒ', 'ðŸ’', 'ðŸ“', 'ðŸŠ', 'ðŸ‹', 'ðŸ‰', 'ðŸ‡', 'ðŸ¥', 'ðŸ¥¥', 'ðŸ', 'ðŸ¥­'];

        function setupMemoryGame() {
            // Determine number of pairs based on difficulty
            let pairs;
            switch(difficulty) {
                case 'easy': pairs = 4; break;
                case 'medium': pairs = 6; break;
                case 'hard': pairs = 8; break;
            }

            // Create pairs of symbols
            let gameSymbols = [...symbols.slice(0, pairs), ...symbols.slice(0, pairs)];
            gameSymbols = shuffleArray(gameSymbols);

            const memoryBoard = document.getElementById('memory-board');
            memoryBoard.innerHTML = '';
            memoryCards = [];
            flippedCards = [];
            matchedPairs = 0;

            // Adjust grid based on difficulty
            if (difficulty === 'hard') {
                memoryBoard.style.gridTemplateColumns = 'repeat(4, 1fr)';
            } else {
                memoryBoard.style.gridTemplateColumns = 'repeat(3, 1fr)';
            }

            document.getElementById('memory-info').textContent = "Find all matching pairs!";
            document.getElementById('memory-info').classList.remove('highlight');

            gameSymbols.forEach((symbol, index) => {
                const card = document.createElement('div');
                card.className = 'card';
                card.dataset.index = index;

                const front = document.createElement('div');
                front.className = 'card-face card-front';
                front.textContent = symbol;

                const back = document.createElement('div');
                back.className = 'card-face card-back';
                back.innerHTML = '<i class="fas fa-question"></i>';

                card.appendChild(front);
                card.appendChild(back);
                card.addEventListener('click', flipCard);
                memoryBoard.appendChild(card);

                memoryCards.push({
                    element: card,
                    symbol: symbol,
                    flipped: false,
                    matched: false
                });
            });
        }

        function flipCard() {
            const index = this.dataset.index;
            const card = memoryCards[index];

            if (card.flipped || card.matched || flippedCards.length >= 2) return;

            card.flipped = true;
            card.element.classList.add('flipped');
            flippedCards.push(card);

            if (flippedCards.length === 2) {
                checkForMatch();
            }
        }

        function checkForMatch() {
            const [card1, card2] = flippedCards;

            if (card1.symbol === card2.symbol) {
                card1.matched = true;
                card2.matched = true;
                card1.element.classList.add('matched');
                card2.element.classList.add('matched');
                matchedPairs++;

                scores.memory++;
                updateScores();

                // Check if game is complete
                let pairs;
                switch(difficulty) {
                    case 'easy': pairs = 4; break;
                    case 'medium': pairs = 6; break;
                    case 'hard': pairs = 8; break;
                }

                if (matchedPairs === pairs) {
                    const infoElement = document.getElementById('memory-info');
                    infoElement.textContent = "Congratulations! You won!";
                    infoElement.classList.add('highlight');
                }

                flippedCards = [];
            } else {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    card1.flipped = false;
                    card2.flipped = false;
                    card1.element.classList.remove('flipped');
                    card2.element.classList.remove('flipped');
                    flippedCards = [];
                }, 1000);
            }
        }

        function toggleDifficulty() {
            const difficulties = ['easy', 'medium', 'hard'];
            const currentIndex = difficulties.indexOf(difficulty);
            difficulty = difficulties[(currentIndex + 1) % difficulties.length];

            const button = document.getElementById('difficulty-toggle');
            button.innerHTML = `<i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Difficulty: ${difficulty.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + difficulty.slice(1)}`;

            setupMemoryGame();
        }

        // Number Guessing Game
        let targetNumber;
        let guessCount;
        let gameActiveGuess = true;

        function setupGuessGame() {
            targetNumber = Math.floor(Math.random() * 100) + 1;
            guessCount = 0;
            gameActiveGuess = true;
            document.getElementById('guess-input').value = '';
            document.getElementById('guess-info').textContent = 'Guess a number 1-100';
            document.getElementById('guess-info').classList.remove('highlight');
            document.getElementById('guess-history').innerHTML = '';
        }

        function checkGuess() {
            if (!gameActiveGuess) return;

            const guessInput = document.getElementById('guess-input');
            const guess = parseInt(guessInput.value);
            const guessHistory = document.getElementById('guess-history');

            if (isNaN(guess) || guess < 1 || guess > 100) {
                document.getElementById('guess-info').textContent = "Please enter a valid number between 1 and 100";
                return;
            }

            guessCount++;
            scores.guess.totalGuesses++;
            updateScores();

            const guessItem = document.createElement('div');
            guessItem.className = 'guess-item';
            guessItem.textContent = guess;

            if (guess === targetNumber) {
                guessItem.classList.add('correct');
                document.getElementById('guess-info').textContent = `Correct! You guessed it in ${guessCount} tries!`;
                document.getElementById('guess-info').classList.add('highlight');
                gameActiveGuess = false;
                scores.guess.wins++;
                updateScores();
            } else if (guess < targetNumber) {
                guessItem.classList.add('low');
                document.getElementById('guess-info').textContent = "Too low! Try again.";
            } else {
                guessItem.classList.add('high');
                document.getElementById('guess-info').textContent = "Too high! Try again.";
            }

            guessHistory.appendChild(guessItem);
            guessInput.value = '';
            guessInput.focus();
        }

        function showHint() {
            if (!gameActiveGuess) return;

            const hint = document.getElementById('guess-info');
            if (guessCount === 0) {
                hint.textContent = `The number is between 1 and 100`;
            } else {
                const lastGuess = parseInt(document.getElementById('guess-history').lastChild?.textContent || '50');
                if (lastGuess < targetNumber) {
                    hint.textContent = `The number is between ${lastGuess + 1} and 100`;
                } else {
                    hint.textContent = `The number is between 1 and ${lastGuess - 1}`;
                }
            }

            hint.classList.add('highlight');
            setTimeout(() => hint.classList.remove('highlight'), 2000);
        }

        // Utility functions
        function shuffleArray(array) {
            for (let i = array.length - 1; i > 0; i--) {
                const j = Math.floor(Math.random() * (i + 1));
                [array[i], array[j]] = [array[j], array[i]];
            }
            return array;
        }

        function updateScores() {
            document.getElementById('tic-tac-toe-score').textContent = 
                `${scores.ticTacToe.x}-${scores.ticTacToe.o}`;
            document.getElementById('memory-score').textContent = scores.memory;
            document.getElementById('guess-score').textContent = 
                `${scores.guess.wins}/${scores.guess.totalGuesses}`;
        }

        // Initialize games
        window.onload = function() {
            setupMemoryGame();
            setupGuessGame();
            updateScores();
        };
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

### Key Improvements:

1. **Modern UI/UX**:
   - Sleek gradient header with score tracking
   - Animated transitions and hover effects
   - Responsive design that works on all devices
   - Font Awesome icons for better visual cues

2. **Enhanced Tic-Tac-Toe**:
   - Added AI opponent with smart moves (uses simple minimax algorithm)
   - Toggle to play against AI or human
   - Score tracking for X and O wins

3. **Improved Memory Game**:
   - 3 difficulty levels (easy: 4 pairs, medium: 6 pairs, hard: 8 pairs)
   - Card flip animation with 3D effect
   - Visual feedback for matched cards

4. **Number Guessing Game**:
   - Guess history with color-coded feedback
   - Hint system to help players
   - Tracks win rate and average guesses

5. **Additional Features**:
   - Persistent score tracking across all games
   - Visual feedback for game events (wins, matches, etc.)
   - Animated celebrations for correct answers/wins
   - Better mobile responsiveness

6. **Code Structure**:
   - More organized and modular JavaScript
   - Better variable naming
   - Improved game state management

The app now has a much more polished, game-like feel while maintaining all the original functionality. The visual feedback makes gameplay more engaging, and the additional features provide more replay value.
